2 cultural economy and the vibrancy of art throughout the state; and
3 WHEREAS, investing in and supporting the arts ensures continued economic growth,
4 educational enrichment, workforce development, and the preservation of Louisiana's
5 irreplaceable cultural legacy; and
6 WHEREAS, Louisiana Arts Day serves as an opportunity to recognize, celebrate, and
7 advocate for the importance of the arts and culture sector and the individuals who sustain it.
8 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
9 does hereby recognize Monday, May 11, 2026, as Louisiana Arts Day in Louisiana.
